<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.9.7">
<l>ilakiya nīṇmuṭi māvali taṉperu vēḷviyil māṇuru vāymuṉanāḷ</l>
<l>calamoṭu mānilaṅ koṇṭava ṉukkiṭan tāṉtaṭañ cūḻntaḻa kāyakacci</l>
<l>ulakuṭai maṉṉavaṉ teṉṉava ṉaikkaṉṉi māmatiḷ cūḻkaru vūrveruva</l>
<l>palapaṭai cāyaveṉ ṟāṉpaṇin tapara mēccura viṇṇaka ramatuvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In fair Kacci surrounded by ponds, the very place of him who,</l>
<l rend="indent">long ago in the form of a dwarf,</l>
<l>Seized the vast earth with trickery at the great sacrifice of Māvali,</l>
<l rend="indent">with a high crown that shined,</l>
<l>Is Paramēccura Viṇṇakaram where bowed the one who conquered</l>
<l rend="indent">the southerner, the king who possessed the earth,</l>
<l>So that many armies perished, and so that Karuvūr,</l>
<l rend="indent">encircled by great, impenetrable walls, feared [him].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
